### =====================================================================
### Follow API  (base route: api/follow/)
### FollowParams: set the relevant id (UserId / ProductId / CategoryId)
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Follow - a user
POST {{host}}/api/follow/Follow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Follow - a product
POST {{host}}/api/follow/Follow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Unfollow - a category
POST {{host}}/api/follow/Unfollow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### ReadFollowers (id = target user)
POST {{host}}/api/follow/ReadFollowers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

